    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a vehicle; it's a preserved fragment of automotive poetry. Cloaked in a finish that drinks in the light like a still mountain lake, this grand tourer exudes an aura of effortless sophistication that modern cars simply cannot replicate. To settle into the cabin is to be embraced by the scent of heritage and the quiet promise of a journey without end. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of high-speed escapes and sun-drenched coastal drives. It possesses that rare, magnetic character that commands a hush as you pull to the curb\u2014a true masterpiece for the discerning soul who understands that a car should be felt, not just driven.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
